 the Arab question in Israeli culture.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2024) 0aHebrew literaturey20th century. 4aLiterature : Hebrew Language and Literature. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Middle Eastern.2bisacsh1 aRon, Moshe, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791486009423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791486009/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles